  "rule_text": "On dark backgrounds \u2014 Dark Gray #567483, Purple #92278F, Dark Blue #262262, Green #01A47E, Teal #0F99BC, or Periwinkle #7B7BED \u2014 the CTA button must use the White filled button (#FFFFFF) with green label text (#01A47E).",
  "intent": "Ensure CTA button contrast on dark backgrounds.",
